financial-analysis-chatbot/
│
├── data/                # Folder for storing raw and processed financial data
├── models/              # Pre-trained or fine-tuned models
├── notebooks/           # Jupyter notebooks for experiments and testing
├── src/                 # Source code for the application
│   ├── backend/         # Flask or FastAPI backend implementation
│   ├── frontend/        # Streamlit frontend implementation
│   ├── utils/           # Utility functions and helpers
│   └── ...
├── tests/               # Unit and integration tests
├── requirements.txt     # List of dependencies
├── README.md            # Project documentation
└── .env                 # Environment variables (not in version control)
